snippet.title: Amber Heard NOT fired? Johnny getting Justice?
snippet.description:
Umberto Gonzalez from The Wrap/Heroic Hollywood posted on twitter that Amber Heard has not been fired from AQUAMAN 2.  His track record is spotty when it comes to DCEU projects, but it does seem like things are moving with the media in favor of Johnny Depp. Especially considering the alleged firing of Johnny Depp by Disney over the PIRATES OF THE CARIBBEAN franchise.
